Hi All;

 After a longer than usual absence--I re-joined. This group tended to be
more ghost hunter oriented, or it seemed that way to me. So just to avoid
arguements I dropped off for awhile. 

 I&#39;ve been trying to combine aspects of Spiricom with boxes, such as mixing
fixed tones in with the radio audio. So far, there does seem to be some
entities that use the tones to enhance voices. The troubel is I have no idea
what frequencies to use, so I started with a set of eight in the leatest
test, tuned to the lowest G major scale that would register on my
auto-chromatic tuner. I have a couple systems that use tow tones. 

